channel.title: Multi-Hit
channel.description: I have no idea what I changed. I was working on Range like a week ago, but that didn't do it because all I changed there was the projectile of Range. Now when I attack a "player" not a "NPC." I hit like rapid hit's... Depending on your str,attck, and defence lvls. With god sword it hits like 40-50 then your dead. It's so fast, it's not fun. And it's not the weapon delay because it's not the only weapon doing it, all of them are, including when your not even wielding one.
